{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229980/extras/02_Main_Header_D2.png?t=1727797453\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This little guy has been having a <i>ruff</i> time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s about time he started working through his issues in\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is Fine \u2013 Maximum Cope!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In This Is Fine \u2013 Maximum Cope your worries aren't just in your head anymore, they've taken physical form, transforming your neighbourhood into several surreal, anxiety-themed realms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2026Each featuring as exciting areas to explore and conquer, linked together in an interconnected map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229980/extras/10_Abilities_Image_1_D2.png?t=1727797453\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you navigate these worlds, you'll encounter a variety of enemies, each an embodiment of everyday worries. Fight off these enemies and traverse hazardous environments, with a toolbox of special abilities such as dog breath and heli-chops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229980/extras/12_Gameloop_Text_D2.png?t=1727797453\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But the real challenge lies in facing the anxiety bosses themselves. Towering manifestation of your deepest fears. Defeat them like the anxiety conquering warrior you are and capture their essence in an anxiety box, Ghostbusters style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stuffing a boss into its anxiety box unlocks new abilities for your character, allowing you to explore new areas and uncover hidden secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">